snippet.title: Geometric sequence and Series : ExamSolutions
snippet.description:
Geometric sequence and Series.
In this video, I'll show you how to find the nth term for a geometric sequence and calculate the sum of the first n terms of a geometric sequence. I'll define a geometric series and its formula.  

YOUTUBE CHANNEL at https://www.youtube.com/ExamSolutions
